user_query: What is the total number of visits across Terminal A, B, C, and E for July 2024?
sql_query: Select Sum(od.Cnt) From OccupancyDaily od Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = od.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31'

user_query: Which terminal was the busiest in March 2024?
sql_query: Select Top 1 f.FacilityName as Terminal, Sum(od.Cnt) From OccupancyDaily od Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = od.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' and '2024-03-31' Group By f.FacilityName Order bY Sum(od.Cnt) Desc

user_query: What was the average number of visits per day across Terminal A, B, C, and E for July 2024?
sql_query: SELECT ROUND (SUM(od.Cnt) / Cast(DATEDIFF(DAY,'2024-07-01' , '2024-07-31') + 1 AS FLOAT) ,2) AS AverageVisitsPerDay FROM OccupancyDaily od JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = od.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' AND '2024-03-31'

user_query: On which days did Terminal A, B, C, and E have the peak usage in March 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName, od.day, Sum(od.Cnt) From OccupancyDaily od Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = od.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' and '2024-03-31' GROUP By F.FacilityName, od.[day] Order By f.FacilityName , 3 Desc

user_query: At what hours did Terminal A, B, C, and E have the highest occupancy in March 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName, ocs.hours, Sum(ocs.occupancy) From OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = ocs.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and ocs.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' and '2024-03-31' GROUP By F.FacilityName, ocs.[hours] Order By f.FacilityName , 3 Desc

user_query: What are the total visits across all terminals for March 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName, Sum(od.Cnt) From OccupancyDaily od Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = od.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' and '2024-03-31' Group By f.FacilityName Order BY F.FacilityName

user_query: What is the busiest restroom across all terminals for March 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, Sum(od.Cnt) From OccupancyDaily od Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = od.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and od.[date] BETWEEN '2024-03-01' and '2024-03-31' Group By f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName Order bY f.FacilityName, 3 desc

user_query: What is the overall feedback across Terminals A, B, C, E for April 2024?
sql_query: Select Sum(Total) From FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-04-01' and '2024-04-30'

user_query: How many 'Excellent', 'Average', and 'Poor' ratings were received in April 2024 across Terminals A, B, C, and E?
sql_query: Select Sum(fbsd.Excellent), Sum(fbsd.Average), Sum(fbsd.Poor) From FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-04-01' and '2024-04-30'

user_query: What is the feedback overview for Terminals A, B, C, and E for July 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName ,Sum(fbsd.Excellent), Sum(fbsd.Average), Sum(fbsd.Poor), Sum(fbsd.Total) From FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31' Group By f.FacilityName Order By F.FacilityName

user_query: Which issue received the maximum feedback across all terminals for July 2024?
sql_query: Select  si.Issue, fbisd.IssueId, Sum(fbisd.Total) from FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbisd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbisd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbisd.SpaceId JOIn SatisfactionIssuesMaster si ON si.id = fbisd.IssueId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbisd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31' GROUP By si.Issue, fbisd.IssueId Order BY 3 desc

user_query: Which room received the most excellent feedback across all terminals for July 2024?
sql_query: Select Top 1 s.SpaceName  ,Sum(fbsd.Excellent) as MostExcellentFeedback From FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31' Group By s.SpaceName Order By MostExcellentFeedback Desc

user_query: Which room received the most negative feedback across all terminals for July 2024?
sql_query: Select Top 1 s.SpaceName, Sum(fbsd.Poor) as MostNegativeFeedback From FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31' Group By s.SpaceName Order By MostNegativeFeedback Desc

user_query: Which restrooms received the most excellent rating in each terminal for July 2024?
sql_query: WITH FeedbackSummary AS ( SELECT f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, SUM(fbsd.Excellent) AS MostExcellentFeedback FROM FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = fbsd.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND '2024-07-31' GROUP BY  f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName),MaxFeedback AS ( SELECT FacilityName,  MAX(MostExcellentFeedback) AS MaxExcellentFeedback FROM FeedbackSummary GROUP BY FacilityName) SELECT fs.FacilityName,  fs.SpaceName, fs.MostExcellentFeedback FROM  FeedbackSummary fs JOIN  MaxFeedback mf  ON fs.FacilityName = mf.FacilityName  AND fs.MostExcellentFeedback = mf.MaxExcellentFeedback ORDER BY  fs.FacilityName;

user_query: Which restrooms received the most poor rating in each terminal for July 2024?
sql_query: WITH FeedbackSummary AS ( SELECT f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, SUM(fbsd.Poor) AS MostPoorFeedback FROM FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = fbsd.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND '2024-07-31' GROUP BY  f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName),MaxFeedback AS ( SELECT FacilityName,  MAX(MostPoorFeedback) AS MaxPoorFeedback FROM FeedbackSummary GROUP BY FacilityName) SELECT fs.FacilityName,  fs.SpaceName, fs.MostPoorFeedback FROM  FeedbackSummary fs JOIN  MaxFeedback mf  ON fs.FacilityName = mf.FacilityName  AND fs.MostPoorFeedback = mf.MaxPoorFeedback ORDER BY  fs.FacilityName;

user_query: What satisfaction issues were reported in Terminals A, B, C, and E in July 2024?
sql_query: Select f.FacilityName, si.Issue, Sum(fbisd.Total) from FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbisd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbisd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbisd.SpaceId JOIn SatisfactionIssuesMaster si ON si.id = fbisd.IssueId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbisd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' and '2024-07-31' GROUP By f.FacilityName, si.Issue Order BY f.FacilityName, si.Issue

user_query: Which restrooms had reoccurring satisfaction issues in Terminals A, B, C, and E for April 2024?
sql_query: Select   f.FacilityName , si.Issue, S.SpaceName , Sum(fbisd.Total) as Count from FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbisd Join Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbisd.FacilityId Join [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbisd.SpaceId JOIn SatisfactionIssuesMaster si ON si.id = fbisd.IssueId Where f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') and fbisd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-04-01' and '2024-04-30' GROUP By f.FacilityName , s.SpaceName , si.Issue HAVING Sum(fbisd.Total)  > 1 Order BY   4 desc

user_query: Which are the top 5 restrooms with the most negative feedback across all terminals for July 2024?
sql_query: WITH FeedbackSummary AS ( SELECT  f.FacilityName,  s.SpaceName,  SUM(fbsd.Poor) AS MostNegativeFeedback FROM  FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN  Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN  [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = fbsd.SpaceId WHERE  f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND '2024-07-31' GROUP BY   f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName), RankedFeedback AS ( SELECT  fs.FacilityName, fs.SpaceName, fs.MostNegativeFeedback, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY fs.FacilityName ORDER BY fs.MostNegativeFeedback DESC, fs.SpaceName Desc) AS FeedbackRank FROM  FeedbackSummary fs) SELECT  FacilityName,   SpaceName,  MostNegativeFeedback FROM RankedFeedback WHERE FeedbackRank <= 5 ORDER BY FacilityName, FeedbackRank;

user_query: Which are the top 5 restrooms with the most positive feedback across all terminals for July 2024?
sql_query: WITH FeedbackSummary AS ( SELECT  f.FacilityName,  s.SpaceName,  SUM(fbsd.Excellent) AS MostExcellentFeedback FROM  FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN  Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN  [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = fbsd.SpaceId WHERE  f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND '2024-07-31' GROUP BY   f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName), RankedFeedback AS ( SELECT  fs.FacilityName, fs.SpaceName, fs.MostExcellentFeedback, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY fs.FacilityName ORDER BY fs.MostExcellentFeedback DESC, fs.SpaceName desc) AS FeedbackRank FROM  FeedbackSummary fs) SELECT  FacilityName,   SpaceName,  MostExcellentFeedback FROM RankedFeedback WHERE FeedbackRank <= 5 ORDER BY FacilityName, FeedbackRank;

user_query: What are the feedback percentages for all restrooms in Terminals A, B, C, and E for July 2024?
sql_query: SELECT  f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, CASE  WHEN SUM(fbsd.Total) = 0 THEN '0%' ELSE CAST(ROUND((CAST(SUM(fbsd.Excellent) AS FLOAT) / CAST(SUM(fbsd.Total) AS FLOAT)) * 100, 0) AS VARCHAR) + '%' END AS ExcellentPercentage, CASE  WHEN SUM(fbsd.Total) = 0 THEN '0%' ELSE CAST(ROUND((CAST(SUM(fbsd.Average) AS FLOAT) / CAST(SUM(fbsd.Total) AS FLOAT)) * 100, 0) AS VARCHAR) + '%' END AS AveragePercentage, CASE  WHEN SUM(fbsd.Total) = 0 THEN '0%' ELSE CAST(ROUND((CAST(SUM(fbsd.Poor) AS FLOAT) / CAST(SUM(fbsd.Total) AS FLOAT)) * 100, 0) AS VARCHAR) + '%' END AS PoorPercentage FROM  FeedBackSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.Spaceid = fbsd.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName IN ('Terminal A', 'Terminal B', 'Terminal C', 'Terminal E') AND fbsd.[date] BETWEEN '2024-07-01' AND '2024-07-31' GROUP BY   f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName ORDER BY  f.FacilityName;

user_query: show the restroom with high usage in dec 2024
sql_query: SELECT TOP 1 f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, SUM(od.Cnt) AS TotalOccupancy FROM OccupancyDaily od JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = od.SpaceId WHERE od.date BETWEEN '2024-12-01' AND '2024-12-31' GROUP BY f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName ORDER BY TotalOccupancy DESC;

user_query: Top 5 slowest restrooms in dec 2024
sql_query: WITH RestroomSummary AS (SELECT o.FacilityId, s.SpaceName, o.RoomName, SUM(o.Cnt) AS TotalOccupancy FROM OccupancyDaily o JOIN [Space] s ON o.SpaceId = s.SpaceId WHERE o.date BETWEEN '2024-12-01' AND '2024-12-31' AND o.RoomName NOT LIKE '%N' GROUP BY o.FacilityId, s.SpaceName, o.RoomName), RankedRestrooms AS (SELECT rs.FacilityId, rs.SpaceName, rs.RoomName, rs.TotalOccupancy, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY rs.TotalOccupancy ASC) AS RestroomRank FROM RestroomSummary rs) SELECT TOP 5 FacilityId, SpaceName, RoomName, TotalOccupancy FROM RankedRestrooms ORDER BY RestroomRank;

user_query: show the hourly satisfaction trend for terminal C on 2nd jan 2025
sql_query:
SELECT DATEPART(HOUR, fbd.CreatedOn) as Hour, fbd.Excellent, fbd.Average, fbd.Poor

user_query: show the hourly satisfaction trend for terminal C on 2nd jan 2025
sql_query: SELECT ocs.hours, SUM(fsd.Excellent) AS TotalExcellent, SUM(fsd.Average) AS TotalAverage, SUM(fsd.Poor) AS TotalPoor FROM FeedBackSummaryDaily fsd JOIN OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs ON fsd.[date] = ocs.[date] AND fsd.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId AND fsd.SpaceId = ocs.SpaceId WHERE fsd.[date] = '2025-01-02' AND fsd.FacilityId = (SELECT FacilityId FROM Facility WHERE FacilityName = 'Terminal C') GROUP BY ocs.hours ORDER BY ocs.hours ASC;

user_query: Top 10 busiest restrooms by terminal pre-security and post-security
sql_query: SELECT f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, SUM(ocs.occupancy) AS TotalOccupancy, CASE WHEN s.Secure = 1 THEN 'Post Security' ELSE 'Pre Security' END AS SecurityClassification FROM OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId JOIN Space s ON s.SpaceId = ocs.SpaceId GROUP BY f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, s.Secure ORDER BY TotalOccupancy DESC;

user_query: List the names of those along with their Jan 2025 usages
sql_query: SELECT DISTINCT od.RoomName, SUM(od.Cnt) AS Usage FROM Facility f JOIN OccupancyDaily od ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal C' AND od.[date] BETWEEN '2025-01-01' AND '2025-01-31' GROUP BY od.RoomName;

user_query: How many unique rooms in Terminal C?
sql_query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.SpaceId) AS UniqueRooms FROM Facility f JOIN [Space] s ON f.FacilityId = s.FacilityId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal C';

user_query: Show the weekly satisfaction issues for terminal A
sql_query: SELECT DATEPART(WEEK, fbsd.date) AS Week, sim.Issue, SUM(fbsd.Total) AS TotalIssues FROM FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN SatisfactionIssuesMaster sim ON sim.id = fbsd.IssueId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal A' GROUP BY DATEPART(WEEK, fbsd.date), sim.Issue ORDER BY Week;

user_query: Show the weekly satisfaction trend terminal c in dec 2024
sql_query: SELECT DATEPART(WEEK, fbd.date) AS Week, SUM(fbd.Total) AS TotalFeedback, SUM(fbd.Excellent) AS ExcellentFeedback, SUM(fbd.Average) AS AverageFeedback, SUM(fbd.Poor) AS PoorFeedback FROM FeedBackSummaryDaily fbd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbd.FacilityId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal C' AND fbd.date BETWEEN '2024-12-01' AND '2024-12-31' GROUP BY DATEPART(WEEK, fbd.date) ORDER BY Week;

user_query: Week over Week usage Comparison in Terminal 3 for Dec 2024
sql_query: SELECT DATEPART(WEEK, od.date) AS Week, f.FacilityName, SUM(od.Cnt) AS TotalOccupancy FROM OccupancyDaily od JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = od.FacilityId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal 3' AND od.date BETWEEN '2024-12-01' AND '2024-12-31' GROUP BY DATEPART(WEEK, od.date), f.FacilityName ORDER BY Week;

user_query: Plot a graph for Which restrooms had reoccurring satisfaction issues in August 2024?
sql_query: SELECT f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, si.Issue, SUM(fbisd.Total) AS Count FROM FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbisd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbisd.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = fbisd.SpaceId JOIN SatisfactionIssuesMaster si ON si.id = fbisd.IssueId WHERE MONTH(fbisd.[date]) = 8 AND YEAR(fbisd.[date]) = 2024 GROUP BY f.FacilityName, s.SpaceName, si.Issue HAVING SUM(fbisd.Total) > 1 ORDER BY Count DESC;

user_query: Show the hourly level details of A1-1L Restroom with poor feedback in dec 2024
sql_query: SELECT ocs.hours, SUM(ocs.occupancy) AS TotalOccupancy, f.FacilityName, ocs.RoomName FROM OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs JOIN FeedBackSummaryDaily fs ON ocs.FacilityId = fs.FacilityId AND ocs.SpaceId = fs.SpaceId AND ocs.LevelId = fs.levelId AND ocs.SiteId = fs.SiteId JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId WHERE ocs.RoomName = 'A1-1L' AND fs.Poor > 0 AND fs.date BETWEEN '2024-12-01' AND '2024-12-31' GROUP BY ocs.hours, f.FacilityName, ocs.RoomName ORDER BY ocs.hours;

user_query: Can you compare the satisfaction issues mentioned in terminal E with those in terminal 2(time period : 10th -16th Feb 2025))
sql_query: SELECT fbsd.date, f.FacilityName, sim.Issue, SUM(fbsd.Total) AS TotalIssues FROM FeedBackIssueSummaryDaily fbsd JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = fbsd.FacilityId JOIN SatisfactionIssuesMaster sim ON sim.id = fbsd.IssueId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal 2' AND fbsd.date BETWEEN '2025-02-10' AND '2025-02-16' GROUP BY fbsd.date, f.FacilityName, sim.Issue ORDER BY fbsd.date;

user_query: Show the observed spike count in terminal A for may 2025
sql_query: SELECT ocs.[dateTime], ocs.Occupancy AS Spike_Count, s.SpaceName FROM OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = ocs.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal A' AND ocs.[dateTime] BETWEEN '2025-05-01' AND '2025-05-31' AND ocs.Occupancy >= 2000 ORDER BY Spike_Count DESC;

user_query: Show the observed spike count in terminal A for may 2025
sql_query: SELECT ocs.[dateTime], ocs.Occupancy AS Spike_Count, s.SpaceName FROM OccupancyCleaningSummary ocs JOIN Facility f ON f.FacilityId = ocs.FacilityId JOIN [Space] s ON s.SpaceId = ocs.SpaceId WHERE f.FacilityName = 'Terminal A' AND ocs.[dateTime] BETWEEN '2025-05-01' AND '2025-05-31' AND ocs.Occupancy >= 2000 ORDER BY Spike_Count DESC;
